frames.caption: A serene lakeside scene features a man in a white robe sitting on rocks by the water, observing a magical whirlpool. In the background, another figure in a robe stands on a wooden pier, gazing at the tranquil lake. The water reflects the soft glow of the evening light, creating a peaceful atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set by a calm lake surrounded by rocks and a wooden pier. The focus is on a man sitting by the water's edge, seemingly engaged in contemplation or meditation. The presence of a whirlpool adds a mystical element to the tranquil setting.

frames.caption: A vibrant scene captures a fish leaping out of a swirling whirlpool in a body of water. The fish's orange scales contrast against the deep blue of the water, creating a dynamic and lively image.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fish emerging from a whirlpool in a vibrant aquatic setting. The water is in motion, creating a sense of energy and movement.
